  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "On August 31, unknown persons who came on a motorcycle in front of the Negombo court fired a gun at a person who had come to hear the case and fled.",
        "Negombo Police said that two people have been arrested with weapons in connection with this incident.",
        "The police further said that they were arrested at around one o'clock in the afternoon today (05) in Kuttiduva area of \u200b\u200bNegombo.",
        "Katwellekama Suresh was seriously injured in the firing by the suspects and was admitted to the intensive care unit of Negombo District Hospital. Due to this firing, a person who was walking on the street was also injured.",
        "The police said that a handgun, five cartridges, a hand grenade, a motorcycle used in the incident and two mobile phones were seized from the arrested suspects.",
        "Ranil Prabhat Roopa Singha is the main suspect arrested. He belongs to Minuangoda Unnarua region.",
        "The other suspect is Muthunayake Khedara Priyantha Sisira Kumara of Muthuwela Kalan Mithunuwewa area.",
        "Police said that the main reason for this shooting incident was love problem and drug problem.",
        "The police also said that the suspects will be produced in court tomorrow (06)."
      ],
